You’re invited to join us today, Monday, 28 October 2024, for a fun and creative Necklace Workshop! It’s a great chance to relax, get crafty, and socialize with friends.
Workshop Details:
Time: 1:15 PM - 1:45 PM
Location: Room 4.03
For a better arrangement, please sign up here: https://forms.office.com/r/er4xcepvp2
Bring a friend along or come solo—all materials are provided. Just bring your enthusiasm and let’s make something beautiful together!
We look forward to seeing you there!
